title: Chances of getting cse
content: Hi. My pessat rank was 11xx and cse at rr closed at 1041. How likely is it that i'll be able to bag cse at rr campus?

comments.body: I think you can get CSE at RR Campus in 2nd Round, as some people leave their seats or convert it to KCET seat .
The cutoff goes up by 300 in 2nd round dw. I'm surprised it hit 1000 in the first.
